snippet: Anthony Davis had 23 points and nine rebounds and Tyreke Evans scored 16 points with a key basket late to lead the New Orleans Pelicans to a 95-92 win over the Boston Celtics on Friday night....

headline.print_headline: Davis, Evans Carry Pelicans Past Celtics 95-92
headline.main: Davis, Evans Carry Pelicans Past Celtics 95-92

lead_paragraph: Anthony Davis had 23 points and nine rebounds and Tyreke Evans scored 16 points with a key basket late to lead the New Orleans Pelicans to a 95-92 win over the Boston Celtics on Friday night.
